Critical Audit Findings
The three biggest issues revealed by the audit:

Split personality — Login is dark/premium, Dashboard is light/plain. First page judges see after login breaks the illusion immediately.
No design system — Every page uses different spacing, radius, and color values. The tokens document gives you the fix.
Missing pages — volunteer/report is a PRD requirement never built. timeline and settings pages are missing for enterprise credibility.
Recommended First Move
Start with Phase 6.5A — paste the globals.css from 

DESIGN_TOKENS.md
 into your existing globals.css. This single change establishes the entire foundation all other phases build on.

Say "implement Phase 6.5A" when you're ready to start.